{"tid":153210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班禪確吉傑布：應培養愛黨愛國佛教人才","createTime":"2017-03-12T11:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T17:06:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ce1fd3fe6fe6f78c171b4383d569fac723a80b","tid":153210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認佛教受商業化影響　有僧人把寺院當「搖錢樹」　班禪確吉傑布：應培養愛黨愛國佛教人才</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170311/s00004/1489253899265SL4_2329FDBBEE1E6B49DB6392EE69D6A008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489253899265SL4_2329FDBBEE1E6B49DB6392EE69D6A008.jpg&h=4a10e8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班禪確吉傑布在北京舉行的政協大會上發言，承認內地佛教受商業化影響，有僧人把寺院當成「搖錢樹」，甚至有假僧人騙錢。他建議政府加強監管，並指寺廟應著力培養「愛黨愛國、清淨修行、心念眾生」的佛教人才。<br />\n<br />\n確吉傑布是全國政協委員及中國佛教協會副會長，他指佛教自從創立以來，對提升人類精神素質和道德修養起到了積極作用，但受商業化衝擊，「有些僧人不守清規，不務正業，追名逐利」，亦有地方將寺院當作「搖錢樹」，更有假活佛、假僧人「用一些似是而非的理論『宣講佛法』」。確吉傑布建議當局建立長效監管機制，依法處理借教斂財的亂象。<br />\n<br />\n確吉傑布表示，每個時期的宗教，都有適應所處時代發展要求的歷史使命。他認為中國佛教界人士，「只有講出符合我國國情、符合社會進步要求的教義闡釋」，才能促進佛教與社會主義社會互相適應，發揮佛教在經濟社會發展中的積極作用。<br />\n<br />\n他提到有寺院「只顧著修金身、建大佛，把殿堂修得金碧輝煌，卻忽視了真正的『肉身菩薩』即優秀僧才的培養」，認為寺廟應減少不必要的建堂修佛，應投放資金培養人才，「著力培養一批愛黨愛國、清淨修行、心念眾生的優秀人才」。<br />\n<br />\n（新華社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170311/s00004/1489242452933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489242452933&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ahv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b7c2413d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489242452933&h=ea2d7ec2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170311/s00004/1489242452933</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312e1d671e282a30ee695881b128fc984db0c8a9","tid":153210,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"老衲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d974c0f618cfb944c6d14f09ee8220dbc895de28","tid":153210,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"達賴死左的話要班禪去揾轉生靈童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47beb7d8f3dc9b7d46e0fc4e2c893e8b995d27bb","tid":153210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858de960ed6797d5a467118276e6f6e3766dc141","tid":153210,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達賴死左的話要班禪去揾轉生靈童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共欽點"},{"pid":"1ce5f9a55bd41405c925fc6a80ccff28d3596dfe","tid":153210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc91ecfb63ec790be3170e20690cdab18c28065d","tid":153210,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>達賴死左的話要班禪去揾轉生靈童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共欽點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以達賴 話自己唔再轉生<br />\n<br />\n不過如果中共求其捉個西藏細路仔話佢係達賴轉生, 都吹佢唔漲<br />\n但西藏人應該唔會信既............"},{"pid":"a1e593d8f6aa88fb8d0d1f74247cf5899e6080c1","tid":153210,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"好一個現代趙志敬"},{"pid":"1d19ec752ed50acef8325436a8bd4986c6ce0822","tid":153210,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite